{"tid":1437981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"冇咗正負皮功能係會搞到有啲混亂","createTime":"2019-08-09T16:13:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T16:55:13.000Z","uid":60293,"like":8,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b8183b8865f4c4ce7cc0d8cd93cef5c1397e1586","tid":1437981,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:13:43.000Z","msg":"其實有大部分人都慣咗睇正負皮<br />\n當限時隱藏咗既話有好多人會唔慣  <br />\n<br />\n呢個時候好易俾對家搵位入<br />\n扮哂野打一大篇好似好到位既post<br />\n再搵十幾個分身去推post<br />\n所以就造成咗依家熱門post咁多唔關事既post"},{"pid":"c338365cc118895e3228d612cf4a214a3281386a","tid":1437981,"uid":60293,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:17:15.000Z","msg":"尤其依家林鄭日日搞記招   對家有大把題材可以帶風向去分散我既地行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   呢幾日大家都有啲俾人混淆咗  但謹記be water<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俾人撓亂過後重新整理思緒  知道邊條先真係我地既主線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">遊行！集會！發夢！</span>"},{"pid":"ae50fb84de1f83bfefa93c52243b77b49b97431e","tid":1437981,"uid":264079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:18:15.000Z","msg":"借位 唔好意思<br />\n<br />\n[反擊]暴政令我不想消費<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436840</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"d43bfe266013223ceabff4e8dd2ba98ee48982bb","tid":1437981,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:21:15.000Z","msg":"建議[red]所有同策略/行動無關既[/size=5]post大家都set咗不推文先回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好俾對家有機會扮自己人再亂打亂我地視線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n先推咗啲有實際作用既post 大家再作決定！"},{"pid":"c488fcca10c042773a340931d88438b0b76e4fc7","tid":1437981,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:22:08.000Z","msg":"建議<span style=\"color: red;\">所有同策略/行動無關</span>既post大家都set咗不推文先回覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"865c5c324b22429548bec786395acedfe055d83d","tid":1437981,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:23:06.000Z","msg":"或者一啲你唔肯定對定錯既post  <br />\n先set咗不推文先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33e01ecf8da8f7f6384ccd7f0696ce47c339db6","tid":1437981,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"先推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"547b5b1f705c8e23792134af77b623f472be7028","tid":1437981,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:23:49.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92323599b015fc5363d1db8cdb4ffe91015ace66","tid":1437981,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:25:11.000Z","msg":"大家 睇下啦"},{"pid":"f50f12c727fbbf080d335ff997be12efe8605122","tid":1437981,"uid":51525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:25:45.000Z","msg":"但係有返正負皮都解決唔到件事<br />\n所以大家唔該要分析 睇文唔用腦 無野幫到你地"},{"pid":"32921f7f83f45f3563c0b74a6d3422110e0d7467","tid":1437981,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:26:07.000Z","msg":"不過我相信過多幾日大家就會慣<br />\n識得自己分應唔應該推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ceb4fb74ddc19e37ffe40347e53a6868a9b881ad","tid":1437981,"uid":131696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:26:26.000Z","msg":"所以要思考下所有post是非黑白<br />\n係時候練下批判性思考"},{"pid":"151804a7581fe0bfecf87b305e51a058dc6db44b","tid":1437981,"uid":60293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f50f12c727fbbf080d335ff997be12efe8605122","tid":1437981,"uid":51525,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:25:45.000Z","msg":"但係有返正負皮都解決唔到件事<br />\n所以大家唔該要分析 睇文唔用腦 無野幫到你地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T16:26:43.000